p: Set a Writ of Habeas Corpus issue as within prayed to be served upon Henry Wiusor Sheriff of Pierce County and upon You C H Foddeu District Attorney of at Olympia & to be returnable before me at Olympia in said Territory On Saturday August 23d 1884 at ten oclock A.M.
Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of Territory
Application of Sam Sock & Jim for Writ of Habeas Corpus
